node.text:
Get inspired to dine alfresco with one look at @lauren.saylor 's outdoor patio! Set the table (and vibe!) with fresh plates, cutlery, napkins, linen throws, updated chairs, and chic glassware. 

In her own words: "One afternoon I decided we weren’t spending another summer without an outdoor dining area. With a few hours of tidying + a few orders from @amazonhome, we finally have the perfect spot to watch a sunset and eat my questionable cooking now. 😆"
 
Love the table and light fixture? We've linked a few lookalikes along with ALLLL the tabletop items and chairs via the link in our bio. Just tap the image to shop! #amazonhome #founditonamazon
